channel.title: The Final Chance to Code! (Free Coding)
channel.description:
I'm so bored that i feel like being nice! so i decided that i will code for some people that need help...so if you need any coding done just post on here ill help you...also if people that are good coders would like to help i would love it =P so ya just post away!
[b]Code Request Form[/b] (use to request a code made for you) [code][b]Code Type: [/b][i]what type of code is this, boolean, case, void, etc?[/i] [b]Code Function: [/b][i]what do you want it do to?[/i] [b]Code Requirments: [/b][i]any requirments for this code to work?[/i] [b]Additional Information: [/b][i]anything else you want me to know about the code, if not put "none"[/i] [b]Explination Of How It Works?: [/b][i]Yes/No[/i][/code]
[b]Want to be part of the team?[/b] (used to join the team) [code]b]What I Am Best At: [/b][i]what are your best java skills[/i] [b]What I Am Worst At: [/b][i]where are you lacking?[/i] [b]What I Want To Achieve: [/b][i]what are you looking for while working for this thread, be honest[/i] [b]Experience?: [/b][i]what are your experiences with java, or any other programming language[/i] [b]Why Should I Be Hired?: [/b][i]why should you be put on the team?[/i] [b](If have)MSN Username:[/b][/code]
[b]The Team:[/b] [i]Final Dawn[/i] [i]TeleNubby[/i]
Like i said before Coder + Boredom = FREE Coding!
